<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>SkillBridge</title>
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Space+Grotesk:wght@500;700&family=Inter:wght@400;500;600&family=IBM+Plex+Mono:wght@500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  :root {
    --bg: #F1F3F6;
    --ink: #17233D;
    --ink-soft: #4C5A72;
    --teach: #0F8B8D;
    --learn: #FF6B5B;
    --gold: #D4A24C;
    --panel: #FFFFFF;
  }

  * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

  body {
    background: var(--bg);
    color: var(--ink);
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  .eyebrow {
    font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--ink-soft);
  }

  h1, h2 {
    font-family: 'Space Grotesk', sans-serif;
  }

  /* ---------- Hero ---------- */
  .hero {
    max-width: 960px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 64px 24px 32px;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .hero h1 {
    font-size: clamp(2.2rem, 5vw, 3.4rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 1.1;
    margin: 16px 0;
  }

  .hero p.sub {
    color: var(--ink-soft);
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    max-width: 520px;
    margin: 0 auto 32px;
  }

  /* ---------- Bridge illustration ---------- */
  .bridge-wrap {
    max-width: 720px;
    margin: 0 auto 40px;
  }

  .bridge-wrap svg { width: 100%; height: auto; display: block; }

  /* ---------- CTA buttons ---------- */
  .cta-row {
    display: flex;
    gap: 16px;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }

  .btn {
    font-family: 'Space Grotesk', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 1rem;
    padding: 14px 32px;
    border-radius: 8px;
    text-decoration: none;
    display: inline-block;
    transition: transform 0.15s ease, box-shadow 0.15s ease;
  }

  .btn:hover { transform: translateY(-2px); }
  .btn:focus-visible { outline: 3px solid var(--gold); outline-offset: 2px; }

  .btn-register {
    background: var(--ink);
    color: #fff;
  }
  .btn-register:hover { box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(23,35,61,0.25); }

  .btn-login {
    background: transparent;
    color: var(--ink);
    border: 2px solid var(--ink);
  }
  .btn-login:hover { box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(23,35,61,0.12); }

  /* ---------- Two sides ---------- */
  .sides {
    max-width: 960px;
    margin: 24px auto 0;
    padding: 0 24px 48px;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 20px;
  }

  .side-card {
    background: var(--panel);
    border-radius: 14px;
    padding: 28px;
    border-top: 4px solid var(--teach);
  }

  .side-card.learn { border-top-color: var(--learn); }

  .side-card .eyebrow.teach { color: var(--teach); }
  .side-card .eyebrow.learn { color: var(--learn); }

  .side-card h2 { font-size: 1.3rem; margin: 8px 0 10px; }
  .side-card p { color: var(--ink-soft); font-size: 0.95rem; }

  /* ---------- How it works ---------- */
  .how {
    max-width: 720px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 16px 24px 80px;
  }

  .how h2 {
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 1.6rem;
    margin-bottom: 32px;
  }

  .steps {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0;
  }

  .step {
    display: flex;
    gap: 20px;
    padding: 18px 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #DCE1E8;
  }

  .step:last-child { border-bottom: none; }

  .step .num {
    font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--gold);
    padding-top: 2px;
    min-width: 32px;
  }

  .step .txt strong { display: block; font-size: 1rem; margin-bottom: 2px; }
  .step .txt span { color: var(--ink-soft); font-size: 0.9rem; }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .sides { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

  <section class="hero">
    <p class="eyebrow">Peer-to-peer skill exchange for students</p>
    <h1>Trade what you know<br>for what you don't.</h1>
    <p class="sub">SkillBridge connects students who can teach with students who want to learn — no fees, just a fair swap of time and knowledge.</p>

    <div class="bridge-wrap">
      <svg viewBox="0 0 720 220" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
        <!-- water -->
        <rect x="0" y="190" width="720" height="30" fill="#E3E8EE"/>
        <!-- left pier (Teach) -->
        <rect x="70" y="120" width="26" height="90" rx="3" fill="#0F8B8D"/>
        <!-- right pier (Learn) -->
        <rect x="624" y="120" width="26" height="90" rx="3" fill="#FF6B5B"/>
        <!-- deck -->
        <rect x="60" y="112" width="600" height="10" rx="4" fill="#17233D"/>
        <!-- suspension cables -->
        <path d="M83 112 Q 360 20 637 112" stroke="#D4A24C" stroke-width="3" fill="none"/>
        <line x1="150" y1="112" x2="150" y2="60" stroke="#D4A24C" stroke-width="2"/>
        <line x1="230" y1="112" x2="230" y2="40" stroke="#D4A24C" stroke-width="2"/>
        <line x1="310" y1="112" x2="310" y2="27" stroke="#D4A24C" stroke-width="2"/>
        <line x1="390" y1="112" x2="390" y2="24" stroke="#D4A24C" stroke-width="2"/>
        <line x1="470" y1="112" x2="470" y2="34" stroke="#D4A24C" stroke-width="2"/>
        <line x1="550" y1="112" x2="550" y2="55" stroke="#D4A24C" stroke-width="2"/>
        <!-- labels -->
        <text x="83" y="145" font-family="IBM Plex Mono, monospace" font-size="13" fill="#ffffff" text-anchor="middle" transform="rotate(90 83 145)">TEACH</text>
        <text x="637" y="145" font-family="IBM Plex Mono, monospace" font-size="13" fill="#ffffff" text-anchor="middle" transform="rotate(90 637 145)">LEARN</text>
      </svg>
    </div>

    <div class="cta-row">
      <a href="/register" class="btn btn-register">Register</a>
      <a href="/login" class="btn btn-login">Log in</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="sides">
    <div class="side-card">
      <p class="eyebrow teach">If you teach</p>
      <h2>List a skill, set your terms</h2>
      <p>Post what you're good at — coding, design, a language, an instrument. Set your level and availability, and accept the requests that fit.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="side-card learn">
      <p class="eyebrow learn">If you learn</p>
      <h2>Find someone, book a session</h2>
      <p>Search by skill, category or level, browse real student instructors, and book a lesson directly. Leave a review once you're done.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="how">
    <h2>How SkillBridge works</h2>
    <div class="steps">
      <div class="step">
        <span class="num">01</span>
        <div class="txt">
          <strong>Create an account</strong>
          <span>Sign up as a learner, an instructor, or both.</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="step">
        <span class="num">02</span>
        <div class="txt">
          <strong>Search or list a skill</strong>
          <span>Browse what's on offer, or post what you can teach.</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="step">
        <span class="num">03</span>
        <div class="txt">
          <strong>Book a session</strong>
          <span>Request a lesson and get confirmed by the instructor.</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="step">
        <span class="num">04</span>
        <div class="txt">
          <strong>Review and save favourites</strong>
          <span>Rate your session and bookmark instructors you'd learn from again.</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</body>
</html>
